#: ../pro/2fa-nextcloud.rst:24
#: ../pro/2fa-nextcloud.rst:24
#: ../pro/2fa-nextcloud.rst:24
#: ../pro/2fa-nextcloud.rst:24
msgid "Now you can tick the box reading “Enable TOTP”. There is shown the TOTP secret which we need to add to our Nitrokey via the Nitrokey App."
