"utilizzando una `Nitrokey Pro 2 <https://shop.nitrokey.com/shop/product/nk-"
"pro-2-nitrokey-pro-2-3>`_ (o `Nitrokey Storage 2 <https://shop.nitrokey.com/"
"shop/product/nitrokey-storage-2-56>`_), e ` autenticazione PKCS#11 "
